# Domain Spec Sync With Data Model

When changing domain/data model structures, keep conceptual specs and checker artifacts synchronized in the same change set.

## Trigger

Apply when changes affect conceptual intent in `backend/app/model/**`, including:

- entity added, removed, or renamed
- relationship/cardinality changed
- ownership/context semantics changed
- lifecycle/invariant semantics changed

## Required updates

- Update relevant diagrams in `spec/domain/*-domain.puml`.
- Update `spec/domain/gen-domain.puml` for cross-domain impacts.
- Keep `spec/domain/domain-sync-mapping.json` aligned.
- Keep `spec/domain/README.md` and `qa/spec_tools/check_domain_sync.py` aligned when behavior changes.
